TextEng: Who are you?
Who you be?
I want to ask you some questions.
Me want ask question.
Why are you helping me?
Why you help me?
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
I'm sorry, I don't understand you.
Me no understand.
What are you trying to say?
Huh?
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
I am no escaped slave! I am a visitor from the distant future.
Text: 저는 탈출한 노예가 아닙니다! 저는 먼 미래에서 온 방문자예요.

TextEng: Me not slave. Me come time travel from future!
Text: 나 노예 아니야! 나 미래에서 시간 여행 왔어!

TextEng: Me not crazy! Me am from future!
Text: 나 미친 거 아니야! 나 미래에서 왔어!

TextEng: I'm not crazy! I really am from the future.
Text: 저는 미치지 않았어요! 정말 미래에서 왔습니다.

TextEng: What can you tell me about the Creator Race?
Text: 창조자 종족에 대해 뭘 말해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout Creator Race?
What is this place you are building?
What you build here?
I am searching for one of the Words of Power.
Text: 저는 권능의 언령 중 하나를 찾고 있습니다.

TextEng: Me look for Power Word.
Can you tell me anything else about this vault?
Text: 이 금고에 대해 더 말해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: You know more 'bout vault?
What was that you said about magical wards?
What you say 'bout magic wards?
Do you know some way I can get into the vault?
You know how me get into vault?
Thank you for your help. I will be going now.
Me thank you for help. Me go now.
